# Job Copilot — Skill Package

This `.skill` file packages the full Job Copilot workflow for installation in Claude.ai.

## Contents

- `SKILL.md` — 8-phase workflow: intake, search, shortlist, resume, cover letter, tracker, interview prep, negotiation
- `references/portal-search-patterns.md` — Portal query syntax, shortlisting signals, red flags
- `references/resume-jd-matrix.md` — ATS keyword logic, bullet formulas, role-type templates

## Quick Start

Once installed, just tell Claude:

```
"Find me jobs as a [role] in [location]"
"Here's a JD — write me a tailored resume"
"I have an interview at [company] for [role]"
"I got an offer — help me negotiate"
```

The skill activates automatically for job search, resume, and career-related requests.

